Part 2 :
 
Give a button to extract the contact list of the user from the phone. 
Ask for "runtime permissions" for contact list access.
Create a CSV format from the contact list. Do this task in the background using rxjava "observable"
Zip the CSV and save it in the storage of the user.
When the zip of the CSV is completed and saved (all of this happens in background) 
- show a "snackbar" to the user informing him that operation has completed.
